{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8577806d-f398-4b51-a2b0-2b93e7506972", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8577806d-f398-4b51-a2b0-2b93e7506972@1.pkg/1772597618208/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597618687", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8577806d-f398-4b51-a2b0-2b93e7506972@1.pkg/1772597618208/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597618687"}, "identifier": "8577806d-f398-4b51-a2b0-2b93e7506972", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查生命有传承。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">C：根据所学，伟大的思想、崇高的信仰、高尚的道德等都是精神生命的体现，在生命的传承中，人类的精神不断积淀和丰富。据此，黄老用实际行动向我们诠释人的精神生命是不断传承的，故C符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">A：说法正确，但在题文中未涉及，故A不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">B：生命的意义在于追求荣誉，此观点错误，故B不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">D：平凡的岗位也能做出伟大的贡献，故D说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">改编）“共和国勋章”获得者黄宗德17岁入伍投身革命，先后参加渡江战役、抗美援朝战争等，为保家卫国浴血奋战。他年逾90，仍坚持把传承红色基因作为自己的使命。黄老用实际行动向我们诠释（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "改编）“共和国勋章”获得者黄宗德17岁入伍投身革命，先后参加渡江战役、抗美援朝战争等，为保家卫国浴血奋战。他年逾90，仍坚持把传承红色基因作为自己的使命。黄老用实际行动向我们诠释（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8577806d-f398-4b51-a2b0-2b93e7506972@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755245352552", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [],